  <title translate="true">articulation points</title>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">A station that is the junction of vectors belonging to two different loop systems is an </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">articulation point</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">. &#160;It is not necessarily a traverse endpoint in either of the two systems.</text></para>
